result.execSummary:
The defendant Franklin E Crabb was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Possession of Methamphetamine [Modifiers: Habitual Criminality], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(g).

For more information, see Wisconsin Statute 111.335 and the Department of Workforce Development's publication, Arrest and Conviction Records under the Law.
